| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-2152 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonforce)"
| comment "Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 1c7d7f56-a4ce-57a6-b8da-16bc6611e13d"
